m, 
<date id="9652369CFF82FFFBB4BBFD55FE3C09E3" box="[222,411,716,738]" pageId="1" pageNumber="268" value="1902-12-20">20 December 1902</date>
, 
<emphasis id="D098CC4EFF82FFFBB5CDFD55FDF609E3" box="[424,593,716,737]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="268">Schlechter 15515</emphasis>
(B-100278232!, isolectotypes A-01154252, B-100278231!, BR-699842!, E-00265564!,
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="E253105CFF82FFFBB4D8FD69FB490804" blockId="1.[136,1452,644,774]" box="[189,1262,752,774]" pageId="1" pageNumber="268">
FI-014506!, G-00388957!, HBG-517024!, K-00739769!, L-0035079!, M-0242296, P-00537659!, 
<collectionCode id="84FD8899FF82FFFBB008FD69FB250804" box="[1133,1154,752,774]" country="Sweden" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15668" name="Department of Botany, Swedish Museum of Natural History" pageId="1" pageNumber="268" type="Herbarium">S-</collectionCode>
09-11256!)
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="E253105CFF82FFFBB4EDFCADFF450F24" blockId="1.[136,1452,820,1243]" pageId="1" pageNumber="268">
The protologue of 
<taxonomicName id="25EC6BDFFF82FFFBB539FCACFE73084C" authorityName="Baillon" authorityYear="1873" box="[348,468,820,846]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Escalloniaceae" genus="Polyosma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Escalloniales" pageId="1" pageNumber="268" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="discolor">
<emphasis id="D098CC4EFF82FFFBB539FCACFE73084C" box="[348,468,820,846]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="268">P. discolor</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
indicates “Oritur in Austro-Caledonia, ubi leger. cl. 
<emphasis id="D098CC4EFF82FFFBB040FCADFB23084C" box="[1061,1156,820,846]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="268">Pancher</emphasis>
et 
<emphasis id="D098CC4EFF82FFFBB0CDFCADFB57084C" box="[1192,1264,820,846]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="268">Sébert</emphasis>
(herb.)”, but the type specimen of this taxon could not be located at 
<collectionCode id="84FD8899FF82FFFBB6A3FCC0FD710871" box="[710,726,857,883]" country="France" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15763" name="Museum National d' Histoire Naturelle, Paris (MNHN) - Vascular Plants" pageId="1" pageNumber="268" type="Herbarium">P</collectionCode>
. There is no reason to believe that it should be located elsewhere since both Pancher and Baillon were affiliated to 
<collectionCode id="84FD8899FF82FFFBB6DAFCE4FD680895" box="[703,719,893,919]" country="France" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15763" name="Museum National d' Histoire Naturelle, Paris (MNHN) - Vascular Plants" pageId="1" pageNumber="268" type="Herbarium">P</collectionCode>
. Type material of 
<taxonomicName id="25EC6BDFFF82FFFBB7C5FCE5FB020894" authorityName="Baillon" authorityYear="1873" box="[928,1189,892,918]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Escalloniaceae" genus="Polyosma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Escalloniales" pageId="1" pageNumber="268" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pancheriana">
<emphasis id="D098CC4EFF82FFFBB7C5FCE5FB020894" box="[928,1189,892,918]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="268">Polyosma pancheriana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, described in the same publication, and also a collection of Pancher, is at 
<collectionCode id="84FD8899FF82FFFBB6B2FC38FD4008B9" box="[727,743,929,955]" country="France" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15763" name="Museum National d' Histoire Naturelle, Paris (MNHN) - Vascular Plants" pageId="1" pageNumber="268" type="Herbarium">P</collectionCode>
. The specimen may be simply misfiled, particularly after the recent refurbishment of this herbarium, and a 
<typeStatus id="3D57AEFEFF82FFFBB6EDFC5CFD4608DD" box="[648,737,965,991]" pageId="1" pageNumber="268">neotype</typeStatus>
will not be designated at this time. The specimen 
<emphasis id="D098CC4EFF82FFFBB174FC5DFA0C08DC" box="[1297,1451,964,990]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="268">Balansa 1780</emphasis>
(P-02582518!) bears the handwritten “est? mon 
<taxonomicName id="25EC6BDFFF82FFFBB6CBFC70FC810F00" authorityName="Baillon" authorityYear="1873" box="[686,806,1000,1026]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Escalloniaceae" genus="Polyosma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Escalloniales" pageId="1" pageNumber="268" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="discolor">
<emphasis id="D098CC4EFF82FFFBB6CBFC70FC810F00" box="[686,806,1000,1026]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="268">P. discolor</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
de herb. Sebert”, which suggests that it has been seen by Baillon.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="E253105CFF82FFFBB4D8FBA8FF4C0FD9" blockId="1.[136,1452,820,1243]" pageId="1" pageNumber="268">
In his description of 
<taxonomicName id="25EC6BDFFF82FFFBB5CEFBA8FCB90F48" authority=", Schlechter (1907)" authorityName=", Schlechter" authorityYear="1907" box="[427,798,1072,1099]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Escalloniaceae" genus="Polyosma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Escalloniales" pageId="1" pageNumber="268" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="podophylla">
<emphasis id="D098CC4EFF82FFFBB5CEFBA8FDE10F48" box="[427,582,1072,1098]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="268">P. podophylla</emphasis>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="867D6DADFF82FFFBB630FBA9FCB90F48" author="Schlechter, R." box="[597,798,1072,1098]" pageId="1" pageNumber="268" pagination="1 - 274" refId="ref4142" refString="Schlechter, R. (1907) Beitrage zur Kenntnis der Flora von Neu-Kaledonien. Botanische Jahrbucher fur Systematik Pflanzengeschichte und Pflanzengeographie 39: 1 - 274." type="journal article" year="1907">Schlechter (1907)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
cited a single collection, 
<collectionCode id="84FD8899FF82FFFBB021FBA9FBFD0F48" box="[1092,1114,1072,1098]" country="China" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:13092" name="Nanjing University" pageId="1" pageNumber="268" type="Herbarium">N</collectionCode>
° 15515. There are apparently two sheets at 
<collectionCode id="84FD8899FF82FFFBB54FFBCCFE980F6D" box="[298,319,1109,1135]" country="Germany" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15534" name="Botanischer Garten und Botanisches Museum Berlin-Dahlem, Zentraleinrichtung der Freien Universitaet" pageId="1" pageNumber="268" type="Herbarium">B</collectionCode>
, both with “ 
<taxonomicName id="25EC6BDFFF82FFFBB5B6FBCDFD6D0F6C" authority="Pillon, 2018" authorityName="Pillon" authorityYear="2018" box="[467,714,1108,1134]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Escalloniaceae" genus="Polyosma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Escalloniales" pageId="1" pageNumber="268" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="podophylla" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis id="D098CC4EFF82FFFBB5B6FBCDFD6D0F6C" box="[467,714,1108,1134]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="268">Polyosma podophylla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="CBAB7135FF82FFFBB6B1FBCCFCB30F6C" box="[724,788,1108,1135]" pageId="1" pageNumber="268" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
” handwritten, but with two different inks. One bears the note “acc. 
<date id="9652369CFF82FFFBB565FBE1FE2C0F90" box="[256,395,1144,1170]" pageId="1" pageNumber="268" value="1903-12-22">22.XII.1903</date>
” (B-100278232) and the other “acc. 
<date id="9652369CFF82FFFBB749FBE1FC3E0F90" box="[812,921,1144,1170]" pageId="1" pageNumber="268" value="1908-01-13">
13. 
<collectionCode id="84FD8899FF82FFFBB729FBE1FCF10F90" box="[844,854,1144,1170]" country="Romania" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:14415" name="&amp;quot;Alexandru Ioan Cuza&amp;quot; University" pageId="1" pageNumber="268" type="Herbarium">I</collectionCode>
.1908
</date>
” (B-100278231). The first one, which is also a better specimen, is chosen as a 
<typeStatus id="3D57AEFEFF82FFFBB582FB05FDF60FB4" box="[487,593,1180,1206]" pageId="1" pageNumber="268">lectotype</typeStatus>
. 
<collectionCode id="84FD8899FF82FFFBB639FB04FDC20FB5" box="[604,613,1181,1207]" country="Romania" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:14415" name="&amp;quot;Alexandru Ioan Cuza&amp;quot; University" pageId="1" pageNumber="268" type="Herbarium">I</collectionCode>
follow 
<bibRefCitation id="867D6DADFF82FFFBB6D9FB05FC200FB4" author="Guillaumin, A." box="[700,903,1180,1206]" pageId="1" pageNumber="268" pagination="174 - 179" refId="ref3576" refString="Guillaumin, A. (1920) Contribution a la flore de la Nouvelle-Caledonie XXX. Plantes recueillies par M. et Mme Le Rat, de 1900 a 1910. Bulletin du Museum national d'Histoire Naturelle 26: 174 - 179." type="journal article" year="1920">Guillaumin (1920</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="867D6DADFF82FFFBB7F7FB05FC6C0FB4" author="Guillaumin, A." box="[914,971,1180,1206]" pageId="1" pageNumber="268" pagination="275 - 278" refId="ref3619" refString="Guillaumin, A. (1939) Materiaux pour la flore de la Nouvelle-Caledonie. LV. - Revision des Saxifragacees. Bulletin de la Societe Botanique de France 86: 275 - 278. https: // doi. org / 10.1080 / 00378941.1939.10834175" type="journal article" year="1939">1939</bibRefCitation>
) in treating 
<taxonomicName id="25EC6BDFFF82FFFBB031FB04FB4A0FB4" authorityName="Pillon" authorityYear="2018" box="[1108,1261,1180,1206]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Escalloniaceae" genus="Polyosma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Escalloniales" pageId="1" pageNumber="268" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="podophylla">
<emphasis id="D098CC4EFF82FFFBB031FB04FB4A0FB4" box="[1108,1261,1180,1206]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="268">P. podophylla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as identical to 
<taxonomicName id="25EC6BDFFF82FFFBB1F2FB04FF430FD8" authorityName="Baillon" authorityYear="1873" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Escalloniaceae" genus="Polyosma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Escalloniales" pageId="1" pageNumber="268" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="discolor">
<emphasis id="D098CC4EFF82FFFBB1F2FB04FF430FD8" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="268">P. discolor</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
